N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 11.132 - Supervisory level qualifications

State Regulations
A supervising public health nutritionist must meet the qualifications for a public health nutritionist and have two years' experience as a public health nutritionist, or have a master's degree in nutrition or public health nutrition from a regionally accredited or New York State-registered college or university, and one year of experience as a public health nutritionist.
